
**********************************************

  apccpp 

  A C++ implementation of apcalc (Aplcon): 
  Contrained least squares fit

**********************************************


For running a standalone example, just type
 $ make -f Makefile.standalone all 
 $ make -f Makefile.standalone install
 $ ./example/example


The compilation requires an installation of the 
Eigen package.
Please provide this either as an inculde path
or as a link or real directory named 'Eigen'.
